Class Observance

  • java.lang.Object
    • biweekly.component.ICalComponent
      • biweekly.component.Observance
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DaylightSavingsTime, StandardTime

    public class Observance
extends ICalComponent
    Represents a timezone observance (i.e. "daylight savings" and "standard" times).
    Author:
    Michael Angstadt
    See Also:
    DaylightSavingsTime, StandardTime, RFC 5545 p.62-71
